      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-11-13T00:58:34Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Yes. UpdateBuild calls are authorized through `buildbucket-update-build-users` group and special tokens from x-build-token header. GetBuild is completely oblivious of that mechanism. If we want to use GetBuild, we\u0027ll need to teach BB to recognize x-build-token for GetBuild.",
